  "body": [
    {
      "content": "你现在将设置系统中的第二个代理",
      "from": 0.18,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 1,
      "to": 2.84
    },
    {
      "content": "文件建议代理",
      "from": 2.84,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 2,
      "to": 5.2
    },
    {
      "content": "该代理将帮助你从结构化数据中选择相关文件以构建领域图",
      "from": 5.2,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 3,
      "to": 11.46
    },
    {
      "content": "让我们进入你正在处理的工作流程",
      "from": 11.58,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 4,
      "to": 15.14
    },
    {
      "content": "你正在第四课中构建结构化数据代理工作流程",
      "from": 15.14,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 5,
      "to": 19.11
    },
    {
      "content": "你在此第五课中创建了用户意图代理",
      "from": 19.11,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 6,
      "to": 22.39
    },
    {
      "content": "你将创建文件建议代理",
      "from": 22.39,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 7,
      "to": 25.02
    },
    {
      "content": "你将采用与第四课用户意图代理类似的模式",
      "from": 25.02,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 8,
      "to": 29.18
    },
    {
      "content": "该代理本身有一个主要目标",
      "from": 29.18,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 9,
      "to": 31.99
    },
    {
      "content": "创建此批准文件列表",
      "from": 31.99,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 10,
      "to": 34.15
    },
    {
      "content": "这将是代理自身需要查看的文件列表",
      "from": 34.15,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 11,
      "to": 38.379
    },
    {
      "content": "并决定这些文件对用户要完成的任务是否相关",
      "from": 38.379,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 12,
      "to": 41.479
    },
    {
      "content": "然后询问用户",
      "from": 41.479,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 13,
      "to": 43.51
    },
    {
      "content": "你批准这些吗",
      "from": 43.51,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 14,
      "to": 44.65
    },
    {
      "content": "如果同意，输出将是执行该操作的批准文件",
      "from": 44.65,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 15,
      "to": 48.66
    },
    {
      "content": "文件建议代理包含许多工具",
      "from": 48.66,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 16,
      "to": 50.94
    },
    {
      "content": "用于查看可用的文件",
      "from": 50.94,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 17,
      "to": 53.41
    },
    {
      "content": "这是所有文件的列表",
      "from": 53.41,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 18,
      "to": 56.57
    },
    {
      "content": "它可以对文件进行采样，进行少量读取",
      "from": 56.57,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 19,
      "to": 60.51
    },
    {
      "content": "它只能读取约一百行",
      "from": 60.51,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 20,
      "to": 62.55
    },
    {
      "content": "然后基于此使用该工具进行推荐",
      "from": 62.55,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 21,
      "to": 66.11
    },
    {
      "content": "称为设置建议文件工具",
      "from": 66.11,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 22,
      "to": 67.97
    },
    {
      "content": "如果用户批准",
      "from": 67.97,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 23,
      "to": 69.71
    },
    {
      "content": "将调用批准建议文件工具",
      "from": 69.71,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 24,
      "to": 72.26
    },
    {
      "content": "这将更新记忆",
      "from": 72.26,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 25,
      "to": 73.68
    },
    {
      "content": "以便在上下文中包含批准文件",
      "from": 73.68,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 26,
      "to": 76.66
    },
    {
      "content": "而不仅仅是建议文件",
      "from": 76.66,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 27,
      "to": 79.18
    },
    {
      "content": "所有这些",
      "from": 79.18,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 28,
      "to": 79.86
    },
    {
      "content": "当然受前一代理工作的指导",
      "from": 79.86,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 29,
      "to": 83.18
    },
    {
      "content": "所有操作均基于用户要完成的整体目标",
      "from": 83.18,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 30,
      "to": 87.63
    },
    {
      "content": "该代理从记忆中获取这些信息而非对话历史",
      "from": 87.63,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 31,
      "to": 92.11
    },
    {
      "content": "因此不依赖于该工具被调用前的对话记录",
      "from": 92.11,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 32,
      "to": 96.37
    },
    {
      "content": "或该代理被调用前的对话",
      "from": 96.37,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 33,
      "to": 98.24
    },
    {
      "content": "此代理将使用获取批准用户目标工具",
      "from": 98.24,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 34,
      "to": 101.36
    },
    {
      "content": "确定用户要完成的任务是什么",
      "from": 101.36,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 35,
      "to": 104.72
    },
    {
      "content": "然后查看文件",
      "from": 104.72,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 36,
      "to": 106.92
    },
    {
      "content": "确定哪些相关",
      "from": 106.92,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 37,
      "to": 108.34
    },
    {
      "content": "并向用户提出建议",
      "from": 108.34,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 38,
      "to": 110.43
    },
    {
      "content": "让我们看看代码",
      "from": 110.43,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 39,
      "to": 112.03
    },
    {
      "content": "你将从常规设置开始",
      "from": 112.03,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 40,
      "to": 113.81
    },
    {
      "content": "导入所需库和之前定义的辅助函数",
      "from": 113.81,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 41,
      "to": 118.11
    },
    {
      "content": "已有这些库",
      "from": 119.64,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 42,
      "to": 120.98
    },
    {
      "content": "我们将连接OpenAI并确保其正常运行",
      "from": 120.98,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 43,
      "to": 125.24
    },
    {
      "content": "哦",
      "from": 127.04,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 44,
      "to": 127.44
    },
    {
      "content": "今天非常稳定",
      "from": 127.44,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 45,
      "to": 128.74
    },
    {
      "content": "是的",
      "from": 128.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 46,
      "to": 129.08
    },
    {
      "content": "我准备好了",
      "from": 129.08,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 47,
      "to": 129.58
    },
    {
      "content": "如何帮助您",
      "from": 129.58,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 48,
      "to": 131.52
    },
    {
      "content": "你将开始构建代理自身的指令",
      "from": 132.289,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 49,
      "to": 135.449
    },
    {
      "content": "现在我们将逐步进行",
      "from": 136.729,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 50,
      "to": 139.56
    },
    {
      "content": "你想要定义代理的角色",
      "from": 139.56,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 51,
      "to": 141.34
    },
    {
      "content": "同时也要设定其目标",
      "from": 141.34,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 52,
      "to": 142.81
    },
    {
      "content": "对于负责建议相关文件的代理",
      "from": 142.81,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 53,
      "to": 147.17
    },
    {
      "content": "我们将称其为建设性批评者",
      "from": 147.17,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 54,
      "to": 149.79
    },
    {
      "content": "正在审查文件列表",
      "from": 149.79,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 55,
      "to": 151.9
    },
    {
      "content": "其目标是建议可用于构建知识图谱的相关文件",
      "from": 151.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 56,
      "to": 158.22
    },
    {
      "content": "然后你可以提供一些执行任务的提示",
      "from": 158.72,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 57,
      "to": 162.2
    },
    {
      "content": "特定的任务",
      "from": 162.2,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 58,
      "to": 163.4
    },
    {
      "content": "当然就是审查文件列表并查看其中",
      "from": 163.4,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 59,
      "to": 167.34
    },
    {
      "content": "哪些文件对基于已批准用户目标的描述中的图谱相关",
      "from": 167.34,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 60,
      "to": 173.84
    },
    {
      "content": "对于每个文件",
      "from": 173.84,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 61,
      "to": 175.22
    },
    {
      "content": "有一个名为样本文件的工具可用",
      "from": 175.22,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 62,
      "to": 178.029
    },
    {
      "content": "可以让代理实际查看该文件内容",
      "from": 178.029,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 63,
      "to": 181.169
    },
    {
      "content": "以确认文件是否包含对实现目标有用的信息",
      "from": 181.169,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 64,
      "to": 185.92
    },
    {
      "content": "我们正在提供",
      "from": 185.92,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 65,
      "to": 187.0
    },
    {
      "content": "同时提示它只需查看结构化数据文件",
      "from": 187.0,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 66,
      "to": 189.76
    },
    {
      "content": "如csv或json",
      "from": 189.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 67,
      "to": 191.93
    },
    {
      "content": "可以用思维链方向收尾",
      "from": 191.97,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 68,
      "to": 195.21
    },
    {
      "content": "此处的思维链包含两个部分",
      "from": 195.21,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 69,
      "to": 197.87
    },
    {
      "content": "首先是准备阶段",
      "from": 197.87,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 70,
      "to": 200.41
    },
    {
      "content": "先调用获取已批准用户目标工具",
      "from": 200.41,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 71,
      "to": 204.44
    },
    {
      "content": "从会话记忆中获取用户目标",
      "from": 204.44,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 72,
      "to": 206.0
    },
    {
      "content": "我们将调用该工具",
      "from": 206.0,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 73,
      "to": 207.32
    },
    {
      "content": "而非直接将信息传递到提示中",
      "from": 207.32,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 74,
      "to": 210.02
    },
    {
      "content": "这鼓励代理使用工具",
      "from": 210.02,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 75,
      "to": 212.399
    },
    {
      "content": "在获取这些信息后",
      "from": 212.399,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 76,
      "to": 214.319
    },
    {
      "content": "我们将提供思维链指令",
      "from": 214.319,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 77,
      "to": 217.19
    },
    {
      "content": "仔细重复这些步骤直到完成",
      "from": 217.19,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 78,
      "to": 219.89
    },
    {
      "content": "以下是代理需要遵循的步骤",
      "from": 219.89,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 79,
      "to": 222.25
    },
    {
      "content": "获取所有可用文件的列表",
      "from": 222.25,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 80,
      "to": 224.579
    },
    {
      "content": "然后针对该文件列表",
      "from": 224.579,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 81,
      "to": 226.399
    },
    {
      "content": "评估每个文件的相关性",
      "from": 226.399,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 82,
      "to": 229.85
    },
    {
      "content": "然后使用建议文件工具将建议文件记录到记忆中",
      "from": 229.85,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 83,
      "to": 235.41
    },
    {
      "content": "此步骤",
      "from": 235.41,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 84,
      "to": 236.39
    },
    {
      "content": "第三步",
      "from": 236.39,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 85,
      "to": 237.11
    },
    {
      "content": "鼓励八和二",
      "from": 237.11,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 86,
      "to": 238.47
    },
    {
      "content": "使用获取建议文件工具获取建议文件列表非常重要",
      "from": 238.47,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 87,
      "to": 243.86
    },
    {
      "content": "代理可能在自身推理和对话历史中意识到",
      "from": 243.86,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 88,
      "to": 249.36
    },
    {
      "content": "文件列表可能是什么以及它认为的建议文件",
      "from": 249.36,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 89,
      "to": 253.08
    },
    {
      "content": "但与其依赖这一点",
      "from": 253.08,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 90,
      "to": 254.82
    },
    {
      "content": "我们希望代理仅使用已保存到建议文件的记忆",
      "from": 254.82,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 91,
      "to": 260.21
    },
    {
      "content": "此处的记忆",
      "from": 260.21,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 92,
      "to": 261.57
    },
    {
      "content": "获取建议文件工具会访问该记忆",
      "from": 261.57,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 93,
      "to": 264.63
    },
    {
      "content": "完成此循环实际上促使模型专注于记忆内容",
      "from": 264.63,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 94,
      "to": 269.21
    },
    {
      "content": "而非对话历史中的记忆",
      "from": 269.21,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 95,
      "to": 272.73
    },
    {
      "content": "然后",
      "from": 272.73,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 96,
      "to": 273.27
    },
    {
      "content": "从工具调用返回的结果是",
      "from": 273.27,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 97,
      "to": 276.15
    },
    {
      "content": "将呈现给用户供其审批",
      "from": 276.15,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 98,
      "to": 278.53
    },
    {
      "content": "如果用户批准",
      "from": 278.53,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 99,
      "to": 279.93
    },
    {
      "content": "则继续说这很棒",
      "from": 279.93,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 100,
      "to": 282.43
    },
    {
      "content": "通常建议的文件",
      "from": 282.43,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 101,
      "to": 284.07
    },
    {
      "content": "但如果用户有反馈",
      "from": 284.07,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 102,
      "to": 285.81
    },
    {
      "content": "返回步骤一并根据反馈重复流程",
      "from": 285.81,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 103,
      "to": 290.65
    },
    {
      "content": "现在可以定义代理使用的工具",
      "from": 291.77,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 104,
      "to": 294.01
    },
    {
      "content": "第一个工具是获取已批准用户目标",
      "from": 295.25,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 105,
      "to": 298.13
    },
    {
      "content": "此功能在提供的工具模块中定义",
      "from": 298.13,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 106,
      "to": 302.07
    },
    {
      "content": "它仅返回存储在状态中的已批准用户目标",
      "from": 302.07,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 107,
      "to": 306.1
    },
    {
      "content": "我们还将导入一个小助手函数",
      "from": 306.1,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 108,
      "to": 308.6
